'''Sekhukhune'' goba '''Matsebe Sekhukhune''', (1814â€“1882), ebe ele ngwana wa kgoshi Sekwati, gape ebe ele kgoshi kgolo ya [[Bapedi]] (goba Marota) ba [[Sekhukhune|ga Sekhukhune]], ko [[Limpopo]] nageng ya [[Afrika Borwa]]. E bile kgoshi ka morago ga lehu la tatagwe ka September 1861,  o be a dula ko thabeng ya Leolo,<ref>{{cite book|last = du Plessis|first = E.J. |coauthors = |title = Suid-Afrikaanse berg- en rivier name|publisher = Tafelberg-uitgewers, Cape Town |year = 1973|pages = 187|isbn = 0-624-00273-X}}</ref> e ago kgona go e shireletja.kgoshi kgolo Sekhukhune naga ya gagwe e thoma ka noka ya lekwe(vaal river) go fihla ka noka ya limpopo (limpopo river).Ba bodikela barile ge  bafihla mo nageng ya ga Sekhukhune ba e abaganya Kage babe banyaka mahumo a naga(gauta) babe baerela leina la Transvaal,ge go fihla maisemane ba e a abaganya gape ba e bitja TWV (Transvaal,Witwatersrant and Vereeniging).Kgoshi kgolo Sekhukhune o lwetje naga ya gagwe goba go fihla Maburu le Maisemane ba kopana ba dira seboka gore ba kgone goka fenya Sekhukhune.

Sekhukhune o kgonne go fenya ntwa magareng ga Maburu le Maesimane bale seboka .Goba go fihla Maburu le Maisemane ba eya gohloma seboka sesengwe le Maswatsi ke ge ba kgona go moswara ba moisha ko toronkong ya Pitori(Tswane)

Leshika la kgoro ya Sekhukhune.
